.SH NAME
SDL_GetGamepadNameForID \- Get the implementation dependent name of a gamepad\[char46]
.SH HEADER FILE
Defined in SDL3/SDL_gamepad\[char46]h

.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
.B #include \(dqSDL3/SDL.h\(dq
.PP
.BI "const char * SDL_GetGamepadNameForID(SDL_JoystickID instance_id);
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
This can be called before any gamepads are opened\[char46]

.SH FUNCTION PARAMETERS
.TP
.I instance_id
the joystick instance ID\[char46]
.SH RETURN VALUE
Returns the name of the selected gamepad\[char46] If no name can be
found, this function returns NULL; call 
